<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="greeting">你好，我是</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">XXX · 资深运营专家</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">5年互联网运营经验 | 内容/活动/用户增长全链路操盘</p>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        擅长从0到1搭建运营体系，主导过千万级曝光活动与百万用户增长项目。
        注重数据驱动与方法论沉淀，能独立完成策略制定、落地执行与效果复盘全流程。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="#works" class="btn btn-primary">查看项目案例</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">联系我</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-tags">
      <div class="tag-card">活动策划</div>
      <div class="tag-card">内容运营</div>
      <div class="tag-card">用户增长</div>
      <div class="tag-card">数据分析</div>
      <div class="tag-card">社群运营</div>
      <div class="tag-card">私域转化</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 64px);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 40px 0;
  }
  .hero-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .greeting { color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .hero-title { font-size: 2.8rem; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .hero-desc {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    max-width: 560px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .hero-buttons { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn {
    padding: 12px 28px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: white; }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #1d4ed8; transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-outline { border: 1px solid var(--border); background: white; }
  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
  .hero-tags {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .tag-card {
    padding: 20px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .tag-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; }
    .hero-desc { margin: 0 auto 36px; }
    .hero-buttons { justify-content: center; }
    .hero-title { font-size: 2rem; }
  }
</style>